Congratulations! You found my secret testing area.
There isn't really much for you to see here unless you want to see what I am working on. You're welcome to stay but if you want to leave, click the button below. Otherwise, keep on scrolling.
Return to the main page

These are progress bars that I intend to add to my resume section to specify skills and how proficient I am in them.

The progress bars are custom components that take arguments for the following:
  • name (title above skill, can be left empty)
  • percent (amount of bar filled, if left empty, a random amount will be filled)
  • color (color of bar, if left empty, a random color will be chosen)
